===Sonohyan utaki lâu Shikina en===
[[File:Naha Okinawa Japan Shikinaen-03.jpg|thumb|right|Sṳt-miàng-yèn ke thìn-è, chhṳ̀-thòng, khiêu-è lau liuk-kok-leù-è]]
